- The integer array parameter `nums` and `removeQueries` must not be null.
- The length of the integer array parameter `nums` and `removeQueries` is equal to `n`.
- The integer array result `answer` is of length `n`.
- The integer result in the `answer` array at index `i` is the maximum segment sum after applying the `i-th` removal.
- The same index in the `nums` array will not be removed more than once.
- The segment is a contiguous sequence of positive integers in the `nums` array.
- The segment sum is the sum of every element in a segment.